- Used `GraphState` TypedDict instead of `AgentState` directly because LangGraph's `get_type_hints()` can't resolve the `AuditEvent` forward reference guarded by `TYPE_CHECKING` (documented in `docs/waves/wave-4-gotchas.md`)
- Renamed node `plan` → `select_agents` to avoid collision with the `plan` state key
- Minimal `ResultSynthesizer` embedded in orchestrator (full version belongs to `workflows/synthesize.py` which is Forbid for this task)

Report at `work/reports/wave-4/05-orchestrator.report.md`.
